{"title":"每日一题：LC236 二叉树的最近公共祖先","date":"2021-06-10T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 11, 2021","L":"06/11/2021","MM-DD":"06-11"},"link":"2021/06/11/刷题日记/每日一题：LC236 二叉树的最近公共祖先","tags":["LeetCode"],"categories":["LeetCode"],"updated":"2021-06-11T02:53:21.717Z","content":"<h1 id=\"每日一题：lc236-二叉树的最近公共祖先\">每日一题：LC236 二叉树的最近公共祖先<a title=\"#每日一题：lc236-二叉树的最近公共祖先\" href=\"#每日一题：lc236-二叉树的最近公共祖先\"></a></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/lowest-common-ancestor-of-a-binary-tree/\" target=\"_blank\">236. 二叉树的最近公共祖先</a>-Medium</p>\n<p>本文参考：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>作者<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/u/jyd/\" target=\"_blank\">KrahetsL6</a>于leetcode的<a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/lowest-common-ancestor-of-a-binary-tree/solution/236-er-cha-shu-de-zui-jin-gong-gong-zu-xian-hou-xu/\" target=\"_blank\">解答</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"dfs\">DFS<a title=\"#dfs\" href=\"#dfs\"></a></h2>\n<p>终止条件：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>当越过叶节点，直接返回<code>null</code>；</li>\n<li>当<code>root</code>等于p或q，直接返回<code>root</code>。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>递推工作：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>开启递归左子节点，返回值记为<code>left</code>；</li>\n<li>开启递归右子节点，返回值记为<code>right</code>。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>返回值：根据<code>left</code>和<code>right</code>，可展开为四种情况：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>当left和right同时为空：说明root的左右子树都不包含p，q，返回null；</li>\n<li>当left和right同时不为空：说明p，q分列在root的异侧（分别在左、右子树），因此root为最近公共祖先，返回root；</li>\n<li>当left为空，right不为空：p，q都不在root的左子树中，直接返回right；</li>\n<li>当left不为空，right为空：返回left。</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> lowestCommonAncestor = <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span>(<span class=\"params\">root, p, q</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(root==<span class=\"literal\">null</span> || p==root || q==root)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> root;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> left = lowestCommonAncestor(root.left, p, q);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> right = lowestCommonAncestor(root.right, p, q);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(left==<span class=\"literal\">null</span>)  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> right;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(right==<span class=\"literal\">null</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> left;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> root;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>时间复杂度 O(N)： 其中 N 为二叉树节点数；最差情况下，需要递归遍历树的所有节点。</li>\n<li>空间复杂度 O(N)： 最差情况下，递归深度达到 N ，系统使用 O(N) 大小的额外空间。</li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"每日一题：LC297 二叉树的序列化与反序列化","link":"2021/06/30/刷题日记/每日一题：LC297 二叉树的序列化与反序列化"},"next":{"title":"数据结构/哈希映射（HashMap）","link":"2021/05/31/数据结构/哈希映射（HashMap）"},"plink":"http://example.com/2021/06/11/刷题日记/每日一题：LC236 二叉树的最近公共祖先/","toc":[{"id":"每日一题：lc236-二叉树的最近公共祖先","title":"每日一题：LC236 二叉树的最近公共祖先","index":"1","children":[{"id":"dfs","title":"DFS","index":"1.1"}]}]}